snippet.title: The Show Begins (Story Trailer) | Dislyte
snippet.description:
The advent of Miracles has struck the world like a double-edged sword; giving rise to a surge of raging Miramons, whilst bestowing people with divine powers.
Among those who have gained new powers, some chose to follow their own desires, whilst others decided to stand up and fight to protect the world from the new threat. 
Today, a newly formed Union squad is heading out to a crisis-ridden place to carry out their first mission...
